.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Food: cucumber, lettuce, pear, radish, grapes
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Food:cucumber == Color:red
2. Food:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Food:lettuce == Beverage:tea
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Pet:bird
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Food:radish is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Beverage:beer
13. Food:pear == Cigar:prince
14. Food:radish is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Food	|   radish	|    lettuce	|    cucumber	|    pear	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
